
'''''The Boy Kumasenu''''' ni filime yasohotse muri  1952 yakorewe muri [[Gana]] n'abakozi ba firime yo mu [[Bwongereza]]<ref>http://www.colonialfilm.org.uk/node/332</ref>. Yakozwe kandi iyobowe na Sean Graham uhereye ku nyandiko ya Graham na John Wyllie.  Amanota yari Elisabeth Lutyens <ref>https://www.tandfonline.com/doi/abs/10.1080/02533952.2013.852826</ref>.  Filime yamenyekanye kandi igira ingaruka mubuzima rusange bwabaturage. Yagaragaje ibimenyetso by'ejo hazaza byatumye bijyana no kurwanya ubukoloni n'impinduka mu mibereho mu bwigenge bushya bwa [[Gana]]<ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/us/film312612.html</ref>. 

== Umusaruro ==
'''''The Boy Kumasenu''''' yari filime ya mbere yagaragaye yakozwe na Gold Coast Film Unit, yashakaga gukora film zombi zigisha kandi zitanga amakuru kugirango zikwirakwizwe muri [[Gana]] ndetse no mumahanga<ref>https://letterboxd.com/film/the-boy-kumasenu/</ref>.   Uyu muyobozi yari Sean Graham, wari umunyeshuri w’umwanditsi w’inyandiko John Grierson, nubwo Graham yahisemo gukora cyane mu mvugo ya sinema izwi. <ref>https://mubi.com/films/the-boy-kumasenu</ref> Umucuranzi Guy Warren yari umwe mu bakinnyi, yakinnye nka Yeboah<ref>https://www.africabib.org/rec.php?RID=35262339X</ref>. 

Yafashwe amashusho mu 1950 na 1951 i [[Accra]], Kedze na Keta , hamwe nabakinnyi batabigize umwuga, ikorerwa i Londres.<ref>http://www.films101.com/16239.htm</ref> Yerekanwe bwa mbere muri [[Gana]] mu 1952 ariko abayikoze bagize ikibazo cyo kuyikwirakwiza muri [[Gana]], kubera imyizerere y’uko Abanyafurika bakunda filime zo guhunga<ref>http://www.films101.com/16239.htm</ref>. Ariko, byaje kugaragara ko ikunzwe cyane.   Yahawe impamyabumenyi n'Iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Venice kandi ryerekanwe bwa mbere mu [[Bwongereza]] mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Edinburgh 1952; yerekanwe no mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Berlin 1953. <ref>https://eprints.bbk.ac.uk/id/eprint/8661/</ref> Yatorewe igihembo cya Filime y'Ubwongereza ya Filime ya Filime nziza mu 1953<ref>https://www.videodetective.com/movie/the-boy-kumasenu-109493</ref>. 

== Umugambi ==
Iyi filime ivuga amateka y’umuhungu witwa Kumasenu wimukiye mu mujyi wa [[Accra]] avuye mu mudugudu muto w’uburobyi, yatewe inkunga na mubyara we Agboh imigani ikabije y’ibitangaza byo mu mujyi. Ashonje<ref>https://www.senscritique.com/film/The_Boy_Kumasenu/43517033</ref>, yiba umugati afatwa n'abapolisi, ariko arokorwa na muganga n'umugore we basanga akora. Agboh agerageza kwiba  Kumasenu muganga, ariko Kumasenu yanga imigambi ya mubyara we.<ref>https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/Cinema-and-Highlife-in-the-Gold-Coast%3A-The-Boy-Sandon/2ef051719a5955a55edccb6fb542f6ba2020f3ee</ref>

